## Next Steps for Deployment

To enable Web Analytics tracking on Vercel:
1. Deploy this application to Vercel
2. Navigate to the Analytics tab in the Vercel dashboard
3. Click the "Enable" button to activate Web Analytics
4. After enabling, analytics data will be collected automatically

## Technical Notes

- Framework: Next.js 16.2.9 (App Router)
- React Version: 19.2.4
- Package Manager: npm
- Analytics Package: @vercel/analytics@2.0.1

The Analytics component is a lightweight client-side script that:
- Automatically tracks page views
- Records Web Vitals metrics (LCP, FID, CLS, etc.)
- Sends data to Vercel's analytics endpoint
- Only runs in production environments

No changes were required to the codebase as everything was already properly configured.
